sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant U as User
    participant JS as Client (AJAX)
    participant C as Controller
    participant S as Service
    participant R as Repository
    participant DB as MySQL

    U->>JS: Submit register form
    Note over JS: e.preventDefault()

    JS->>C: POST /auth/register (JSON)

    activate C
    C->>C: Validate & map to RegisterRequestDTO

    alt Invalid input
        C-->>JS: 400 Validation Error
    else Valid input
        C->>S: register(dto)
        activate S

        S->>S: hashPassword()

        S->>R: saveUser()
        activate R
        R->>DB: INSERT user

        alt Username duplicated
            R-->>S: error
            S-->>C: ApiException
            C-->>JS: 409 Username exists

        else Success
            S->>R: saveProfile()
            R->>DB: INSERT profile

            alt Profile duplicated
                R-->>S: error
                S-->>C: ApiException
                C-->>JS: 409 Profile exists

            else Success
                S-->>C: RegisterResponseDTO
                C-->>JS: 200 OK
                JS->>U: Show success message
            end
        end

        deactivate S
    end
    deactivate C

    Note over JS,DB: 500 Internal Server Error (unexpected)